metadata.name: Enter the House of Crypto - Original
metadata.description:
Original paper mosaic artwork by Shando Z. The foundation piece of the Papered Peace - ETHOC nft collection. This is the final artwork after it has been covered in epoxy, forever changing it appearance. Created using hundreds of tiny pieces of different papers on a 18x24 inch panel.

This mint includes shipment of the physical 18" x 24" (45.72cm x 60.96cm) artwork from the artist and an additional NFT of the artwork before the epoxy was poured.

[Papered Peace Website](https://www.paperedpeace.com/)
